cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you reference the Kronaxis research stack, please cite the underlying
  preprints. DYNAMICS-8 is the personality framework; KPM v17.10 is the
  current production election-forecasting methodology that builds on top.
type: software
title: "awesome-kronaxis-research — The Kronaxis Research Stack"
abstract: >-
  An index repository for the Kronaxis research stack: the DYNAMICS-8
  personality framework, the Panel Studio synthetic-panel engine, the
  KPM-1 pre-registered election projections, the Kronaxis Polling Method
  (KPM v15.1 + v17.10), and the Kronaxis Router LLM infrastructure.
  Provides a single entry point with descriptions, DOIs, and links for
  researchers landing here.
